name: Hakari Hanazono Kimi no Koto ga Daidaidaidaidaisuki na 100-nin no Kanojo
description: Rentarou Aijou memiliki segalanya: penampilan, kecerdasan, keterampilan atletik, dan popularitas di antara teman sebaya dan para mentor. Sayangnya, tidak ada dari kualitas-kualitas ini yang membantu Rentarou dalam kehidupan cintanya. Pada hari kelulusan SMP-nya, dia sekali lagi ditolak oleh seorang gadis yang dia akui, meraih penolakan yang ke-100 berturut-turut. Down on his luck, he goes to a matchmaking shrine and wishes to finally get a girlfriend in high school.
author: Rikito Nakamura

chapters.sinopsis: Hyakkano and 君のことが大大大大大好きな100人の彼女

name: Inda Karane (院いん田だ 唐から音ね)
description: Inda Karane (院いん田だ 唐から音ね Inda Karane?) is a first year student at Ohananomitsu High School in Class 1-4 as well as Aijou Rentarou's first two girlfriends (alongside with Hanazono Hakari). She is an extreme tsundere, reacting violently to the compliments given by her boyfriend or her fellow girlfriends. However, she can occasionally be straightforward and honest with how she feels, though this takes great effort.
author: Miyu Tomita

chapters.sinopsis: Karane has golden, shiny hair, divided into two pigtails with green bows, a flat chest and hazel eyes, and a slender figure. She wears a typical high school uniform with a beige sweater, underneath a white shirt and navy-blue skirt, as well as loafers with loose knee-length socks. She is quoted to be beautiful with desirable features, and at points, is hit on by other guys, much to her annoyance and Rentarou's jealousy.

name: Kirara Genshin
description: Desainer terkenal Chiori adalah pembuat model pakaian karakter Kirara di game Genshin Impact. Chiori menciptakan model pakaian Kirara dengan prinsip 'Memakaikan bunga-bunga yang indah ke tubuh seseorang dengan nyaman'
author: Chiori

chapters.sinopsis: Kirara adalah karakter baru yang diperkenalkan dalam update versi 3.7 Genshin Impact. Kirara adalah nekomata yang bekerja sebagai kurir di Komaniya Express, perusahaan pengiriman terkenal di Inazuma. Kirara merupakan pengguna elemen dendro pertama dari Inazuma.
